{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC04_JUR_110.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x18,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "If I remember correctly, the dragon we saw before was somewhere around here. He sure was big..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "He is the last one left in this area."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I see. In that case, I guess we got to see a rare sight."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "But why aren't there any other dragons?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "They look so strong..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yes. By nature, since dragons are so strong individually, they have little need to breed for survival purposes."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "However, in recent times, they have been slain by humans, and their numbers have decreased sharply."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Even the strongest dragons are being hunted by humans..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "And even dragons are no match for great number of armed humans."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x10,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "So many were exterminated that their numbers dwindled, and now he's the last one."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I remember you saying something about killing of live stock..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Naturally, dragons and humans have mutual enmity for each other."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "The dragon we saw before...he's no different. Very recently, cattle were taken from my village."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Eeh? Really? E-Even Nanaca's cows!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "No, Nanaca was far away at the time, so she was okay, as well as her cows."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Good..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "An aged dragon is cunning and cautious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I don't know where he goes to roost."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "He appears out of nowhere in human villages when he gets hungry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "So we never know when he might come...<CR>That's...scary."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "That's why humans hunt dragons. It's too dangerous to have them for a neighbor."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I can't let him stay on the loose like this. Someday, I will fight that dragon."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "That is the fate that has been handed down to me by my family..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "(Juris is really serious about taking down that dragon...)"
        }
    ]
}